  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients 18 years or older

          2. After allogeneic transplantation

          3. Grade III or IV acute GVHD

          4. No psychiatric contra-indication

          5. Informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. History of psychosis

          2. Asthma

          3. Known allergy to cannabis constituents
      </textblock>
